>=20
> - GSoC ideas (https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/wiki/GSoC-ideas <https:/=
/github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/wiki/GSoC-ideas>): this is a list of ideas for =
projects that students could do. It needs to be filled up and then maintain=
ed, so that by next year at least, we actually have something to show googl=
e.
>=20
> - GSoC Application (https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/wiki/GSoC-applicat=
ion <https://github.com/ocaml/ocaml.org/wiki/GSoC-application>): a hastily =
filled out application covering the questions google expects answered. This=
 should also be maintained so that it's pretty much ready to go.
